    <briefdescription>
<para>Container for Renesas ELC information specified in devicetree. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This type contains a pointer to a Renesas ELC device, along with the peripheral ID and event ID used to configure a link between peripherals via the Event Link Controller.</para>
<para>This structure is typically initialized using devicetree macros that parse phandle-array properties referencing ELC instances. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
